items.title: JNJ's Nipocalimab Gets FDA's Fast Track Tag for Sjogren's Disease
items.description: The FDA bestows a Fast Track designation to Johnson & Johnson's nipocalimab for treating moderate-to-severe Sjogren's disease in adults.
